features: 【AI Powered Human Motion & Sound Detection】Arenti wifi camera supports motion detection and push alert to monitor your pet. When your pet destroys your home, will send alert message on your phone to let you know (Only support 2.4GHz WiFi, not 5G). Mini camera can be installed anywhere such as the living room, kitchen, and office. Space efficient design helps you acquire a wider view angel.

【Remote Monitoring & Two-Way Audio】Built-in Mic and speaker offer you smooth talk with your pets anytime, anywhere, always keeping your pet in sight no matter you're in the kitchen or away from home. Home camera also can scare off intruders with audio and protect your property.

【1080P Full HD & Enhanced Night Vision】Arenti indoor security camera support 1080p (max) resolution and enhanced night vision(up to 10m/32ft). You can see the delicate movements of your pet clearly. It also supports 180-second(max) video recording and playback, longer than most other cameras on the market. If you use an SD card, it also supports full-day recording, which makes the M1 smart home security camera a 24-hour guardian of your pet, family no matter day or night.

【Set, Monitor, and Share All via free App】You can turn on or off the camera or indicator light through the APP. You can also set the timing. You can set, monitor, and control all your cameras in one app. You can also invite your family, friends, or anyone you care to download the app and share your precious moments. The sharing can also be canceled at any time.

【Support Full-day Recording & SD Storage 】The Arenti camera also supports full-day recording with FAT32 Micro SD cards (not included) up to 256G. With advanced E2EE video encryption, Arenti Cloud Service securely stores your data on AWS by Amazon.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Record every moment of your life! Arenti M1 Indoor Security Camera Arenti indoor camera is aiming to offer global users easier, safer, and smarter home security products with the perfect combination of cutting-edge design, advanced technology & user-friendly functions.
Remote Monitoring. You can download the Arenti app on your phone to control and view the camera. Check what happened your home according to the time and movement status.

Previous page Real-time Motion and Sound Detection If M1 indoor camera detects abnormal movements or sounds, it will push an alarm immediately. Two-way calls with your baby/elderly/pet can be made anytime, anywhere. 1080p HD Vision Provide you with 1080p clear image quality and 32ft high-definition night vision function. Baby and pet camera with phone app, share life with your family！ 90-days free Cloud Storage. Supports micro-SD with up to 128GB storage capacity. Next page 1 Real-time Alert 2 Two-way Audio 3 1080P HD Video 4 Share with Your Family 5 Flexible Storage Options
Mini Size Design, Can be Installed Anywhere.

Easy to set up: Download App & Plug in the Camera Download Arenti APP Download "Arenti" app from App Store or Google Play. Or scan the QR code on the user manual. Reset with a Pin Reset the camera, and then the red light flashes. Scan the QR Code Place the QR code auto-generated by your phone in front of the camera until the camera beeps. Connect Successfully After hearing the beep sound, Click the Button and Wait about 20 seconds, the Set up is Finished.

How do I connect the camera to wifi? Step 1: Download "Arenti" app. Step 2: Click the '+' icon on the page & choose M1 & enter the correct wifi information. Step 3: Scan the QR Code on App. After the beep sound, Click the Button & Wait for 20 seconds, the Set up is Finished. What should I notice when connecting to the camera? The device only supports 2.4G, if the router is a Dual Band, please disable 5g, and then turn on 5g after the connection. How do you turn off the bright blue light in the app? APP-Device(tap device to live video page)-Settings-Basic Function-Network Indicator-Disabled Does the camera rotate? Can it be used without power? The camera does not rotate automatically, the angle can be adjusted manually. Needs to be plugged in all the time and connected to the network to use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great small form factor
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this ARENTI Indoor Security Camera, 1080P Dog Cam Pet Camera for Home Security, 2.4G WiFi Wired Camera for Baby/Elder/Pet, Motion Detection, Night Vision, 2-Way Talk, Works with Alexa & Google Assistant from the seller Arenti Smart US for the price of $24.99 and it was shipped by Amazon Prime.After using a LOT of different security cameras over the years I am completely done with the whole house systems and I much prefer these wireless app controlled devices. They work in exactly the same fashion as the big systems, but you buy them one at a time and place them wherever you want as long as there's a nearby power outlet. In the case of there not being one close I just buy a long Type A Male to Type A Female USB Extension and the long thin cable is way better than running this stuff through my attic or crawl space and drilling holes.This particular camera went out in my garage. The app was a little different than some of my other cameras, but it is PERFECT for there. It's small so I was able to get it right up against the ceiling and get a clear view of my entire garage as well as the door so I can see if I ever accidentally leave it open.I've personally used this to watch the garage when I received a delivery of tile that came before I got home. Delivery guy called and I have a remote garage door opener so I opened the garage, he wheeled the pallets into my garage and I was able to watch the whole thing. Then when he was done I just closed up the garage and house was all safe and secure again.The image quality is good, especially for a $25 camera. I've had some $50-$60 cameras that have a similar quality and however much my Nest doorbell camera is, that thing is not any better than this and I think was a couple hundred bucks.Make sure to put in your own micro sd card for memory.
